quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  21,94,"N’uwuzogira ibikorwa vyiza mugihe nawe ari umu Isilamu uyo muntu ntazo kwankirwa kumwete wiwe yagize, mu vy’ukuri ivyo yagize twebwe tuzovyandika"
  21,95,Kirazira yuko igisagara twahoneje yuko abo bantu bazogaruka iwacu
  21,96,Kugeza aho hazobohorwa uwitwa Ya’ajuja na Ma’ajuja nabo bamanuka bava kumisozi yose
  21,97,"Hazoshika kuri rya sango ry’ukuri, ari naho hazosokoka amaso y’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bavuga bati:- Yoh! Ntankeka twebwe twari mubiyibagiye nibi bintu, ahubwo twarahemukiye imitima yacu"
  21,98,"Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe hamwe nivyo musenga mukureka gusenga Imana yanyu y’ukuri, muzoba muri inkwi z’uwo muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, namwe muzowu shikira"
  21,99,"Iyo aba ari izindi Mana, ntibari gushikirwa nuwo muriro witiriwe Jahannamu, n’ingene bangana bose bazoba bari muri uwo muriro udahera"
  21,100,"Muri uwo muriro udahera bazo komerayo induru, nabo muriwo ntibazo kwumva"
  21,101,"Mu vy’ukuri abo ineza yacu yashikiye, bazoba bari kure nuwo muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  21,102,"Ntibazo kwumva isumo ryuwo muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, nabo bazowubamwo mubuzima bwabo bwose kuvyo bipfuriza imitima yabo"
  21,103,"Ntuzoba tetereza ubwo bwoba buhanitse, n’Abamarayika bazoba sanganira bababwire bati:- uwu niwo wamusi wanyu mwamye muraganirwa"
  21,104,"Umusi tuzozinga amajuru nkakumwe tuzinga urupapuro twandikako, nkuko twatanguye irema ryambere niko tuzorisubira mwo kurigira, iyi n’indagano iri hejuru yacu kandi ntankeka nitwebwe tubigira"
  21,105,Mu vy’ukuri twaranditse mugitabu c’Imana ca Zaburi munyuma yaho twandika k’urubaho rubitswe neza yuko iy’Isi izosigirwa abantu banje beranda
  21,106,Mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ubutumwa ku bantu bagira amasengesho y’ukuri
  21,107,Natwe ntitwa kurungitse atari uko wobabera impuhwe ku bantu bose
  21,108,"Vuga uti:- jewe sinahawe ubu butumwa atari uko Imana yanyu ari Imana imwe yonyene rudende gusa, mbega muremeye kuba aba Isilamu"
  21,109,"Nibatemera kuri ivyo wewe n’uvuge uti:- ndabamenyesheje bimwe vy’ukuri yuko jewe atabumenyi mfise bw’ibiri hafi canke ibiri kure y’ivyo mwahawe ko indagano"
  21,110,Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’imvugo iri k’umugaragaro hamwe n’ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza
  21,111,Kandi ntanakimwe nomenya yuko ari urwanko kuri mwebwe n’umunezero kugeza kumwanya mugufiya gusa
  21,112,"Yavuze ati:- ewe Muremyi wanje nubacire urubanza rw’ukuri, n’Umuremyi wacu niwe nyene impuhwe asabwa imfashanyo kuri ivyo muvuga vyose. mito"